name: Ordinal Tomcats
description: Ordinal Tomcats is an exclusive NFT collection consisting of 100 unique Tomcats inscribed on the Bitcoin blockchain. As one of the first NFT collections on this chain, providing a rare and coveted addition to any digital collection. Whether displayed as an emblem of personal identity or used as a symbol of prestige within the NFT community, Ordinal Tomcats offers a one-of-a-kind opportunity to own a piece of blockchain history.
